§ specs/53_EXISTING_FEATURES_CATALOG · already-built loa-host modules · undocumented-surface
  ← survey of pre-existing infrastructure Apocky may not realize is shipped
  ← @ HEAD d311de1 · post-18-merges · 3 agents flying

§I PURPOSE
  Apocky asked "feed pre-authored data" thinking we need to build new pipelines ;
  HALF the pipelines already exist · they just need to be invoked or surfaced.
  This spec catalogs what's already built so we don't reinvent.

