  ⟦
    camera             ← genre-fluid 4-mode camera (Fps · ThirdPerson · Iso · TopDown)
    geometry           ← ?
    material           ← ?
    pattern            ← ?
    room               ← test-room scene
    stokes             ← Navier-Stokes fluid? for wind/water
    spectral_bridge    ← CPU-bake CRH spectral-LUT bridge
    input              ← raw input handling
    input_genre_fluid  ← multi-source router (KB/Mouse · Gamepad · Touch · DualSense)
    movement           ← character movement
    physics            ← physics step
    mcp_server         ← TCP JSON-RPC server (Claude live interface)
    mcp_tools          ← MCP tool implementations
    telemetry          ← JSONL-event emission
    dm_director        ← Director state machine (entropy-gradient driven · per LoA-v10 §06)
    gm_narrator        ← Narrator state machine
    dm_runtime         ← runtime mutation hooks
    gm_persona         ← persona-state for narrative-arc
    dm_arc             ← 5-phase arc state-machine (Discovery · Tension · Crisis · Catharsis · Quiet)
    ui_overlay         ← textured-quad UI pipeline · catalog-buildable
    fps_hud            ← crosshair · ammo · radar · health · objective · damage-floaters
    polish_audit       ← perf-budget tracker · WCAG color-contrast · loading-spinner
    perf_runtime_check ← AdaptiveDegrader integration
    fps_pipeline       ← triple-buffered frame-slot ring · pre-allocated cmd-buffer pool
    wired_fps_pipeline ← MCP-style accessor over fps_pipeline
    snapshot           ← PNG encode + tour-pose registry + golden-image diff
    fidelity           ← global GPU fidelity-report
    cfer_render        ← Ω-field volumetric-raymarched (PRIMARY substrate path)
    sense              ← 20+ sense.* MCP tools (visual · audio · spatial · interoception ·
                          diagnostic · temporal · causal · network · environmental)
    gltf_loader        ← pure-Rust GLTF/GLB → Vertex (no native deps)
    spontaneous        ← TEXT-SEEDED CONDENSATION (intent-text → seed-cells → ω-stamps →
                          ManifestationDetector → STRESS-OBJECT condenses-at-cell)
    intent_router      ← (suggested by name)
    substrate_render   ← Crystal-128 + KAN-multiband + dyn-res + AMOLED-deep
    dynamic_resolution ← Q0.16 adaptive resolution-scaler
    display_profile    ← 5-profile auto-detect + per-LUT contrast-stage
    fps_pipeline       ← (above)
    content_pipeline   ← LOA_CONTENT_PIPELINE=1 wires DMGM-council → procgen → crystals
  ⟧

§I CRITICAL-UNDERAPPRECIATED-FEATURES
  ⟦
    spontaneous (text-seeded condensation) :
      FFI : extern "C" __cssl_world_spontaneous_seed(text_ptr, text_len, x, y, z)
      MCP : world.spontaneous_seed { text, origin }
      WIRED : window.rs line 482 drains queue every event-loop tick
      EVOLVES : sow_spontaneous_intent → SeedCells → field-stamps → cfer-render →
                ManifestationDetector::scan_rising_edges → STRESS-OBJECT
      USAGE : send "blue crystal forest" via MCP and watch it materialize

    gltf_loader : full pure-Rust GLTF/GLB parser
      pub fn load_gltf(bytes: &[u8]) -> Result<Vec<Vertex>, GltfErr>
      ALREADY-AVAILABLE for any external 3D model
      USAGE : feed Khronos GLTF Sample Models · output to substrate-input

    sense (MCP-tools 20+) :
      Lets external Claude PERCEIVE the live engine across 9 axes
      Already documented · already wired
      USAGE : connect Claude Desktop via MCP → query sense.visual, sense.spatial · etc

    cfer_render : volumetric raymarched (NOT triangle-based)
      Aligns with Apocky's "raymarched-SDF-PRIMARY" axiom
      Catalog-buildable + runtime-feature-GPU upload

    fps_hud + ui_overlay :
      Full HUD suite is ALREADY built · world-anchored capable
      Could be activated for game-feel
  ⟧

§I HOW-TO-USE-EXISTING-FEATURES (no new code required · just env-vars + MCP-calls)
  ⟦
    SPONTANEOUS-SEED via MCP :
      1. Connect Claude Desktop to LoA's MCP TCP server (default 127.0.0.1:3001)
      2. Call world.spontaneous_seed { text: "ancient stone arch covered in glowing moss",
                                          origin: [10.0, 0.0, 5.0] }
      3. Watch substrate evolve · STRESS-OBJECT condenses at cell
      4. Sequential calls accumulate world-state · purely-local · sovereignty-respecting

    GLTF-LOAD via FFI/MCP :
      1. external 3D model (CC-licensed · e.g. Khronos sample) → bytes
      2. Either : call gltf_loader::load_gltf in catalog-test
                 OR : MCP-call world.spawn_gltf { bytes_path, world_pos }
      3. parsed Vertex array goes into dynamic-mesh path

    PROCGEN-CONTENT-WIRE :
      $env:LOA_CONTENT_PIPELINE = "1" ; LoA.exe
      DMGM-council generates procgen-output every-second
      replaces shell-seed substrate with content-driven crystal-vector

    SPECIALIST-PERSIST :
      ~/.loa/specialist_<role>.bin auto-saved · auto-loaded
      DM/GM/Collaborator/Coder accumulate observations across LoA-restart

    MYCELIUM-FEDERATE (foundations only · explicit-opt-in) :
      $env:LOA_MYCELIUM_LOAD = "1" ; LoA.exe
      reads ~/.loa/peer_cache.json · merges KanBiasShard records · sigma-mask-verified
  ⟧

§I MISSING-SURFACE-AREAS (next-wave-targets)
  ⟦
    1. KEYBOARD text-input → spontaneous_seed (currently MCP-only)
    2. VOICE input → intent_router → spontaneous_seed (whisper-rs not-wired)
    3. KEYBOARD-shortcut to invoke gltf_loader on a path (currently MCP-only)
    4. UI-overlay panel showing the 13 coherence-axes-state
    5. fps_hud activation (HUD is built · not enabled by default)
    6. menu-system (illuminated-manuscript-style · per LoA-v10 §08)
  ⟧

§I IMPLICATIONS
  Apocky's ask "feed pre-authored data" is partially-answered-by-existing-code :
    ◐ MCP-callable spontaneous-seed exists (text → world)
    ◐ gltf_loader exists (3D-data-from-external-source)
    ◐ procgen-pipeline + dm-procgen-bridge exists (algorithmic-generation)
    ◐ asset-loader manifest exists (CC-licensed sources catalog)
    ○ keyboard/voice user-text-input still missing (UI-not-wired)

